2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper uses a Generative Adversarial Network (GAN) for image generation, which is a popular technique in AI.
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses machine learning techniques to train the GAN model.
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with generating images of human poses, which is relevant to the field of computer graphics.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with generating images of people, which is relevant to the field of multimedia.
